         <abstract><p>The Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel is a collection of 12 homilies in honour of <persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/>, one for each month.
            After the homilies, each monthly lecture contains a miracle, a comemmorative notice from the <title ref="LIT2375Synaxa"/> and a salām to <persName ref="PRS7049Michael"/>. 
         The order and the absence of these texts change frequently.
         <listBibl type="secondary">
